      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着股市暴跌加剧，明星中国基金在 2024 年将陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/star-china-funds-turn-to-duds-in-2024-as-stocks-rout-gets-ugly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些经历过去年中国股市暴跌的境内基金正在失去光芒，因为最近的损失突显了投资于趋势可能迅速逆转的 8 万亿美元市场所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/star-china-funds-turn-to-duds-in-2024-as-stocks-rout-gets-ugly</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:49:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国正在采取一切措施拯救遭受重创的股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/everything-china-is-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当局试图阻止市场连续第四年暴跌，中国加大了救援力度，中国股市已从 7 万亿美元的暴跌中开始复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-07/everything-china-is-doing-to-rescue-its-battered-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:36:45 GMT</pubDate>
